author: chirino
msg: Fixes APLO-318: Large transactions sending persistent messages hang.
The queue's max inbound memory buffer was limiting how large the transaction could be.

author: chirino
msg: Make sure we release the UoW for messages that expired before they were enqueued.  This was causing the pending_store counter on the store to grow.
